snippet.title: Alchemic Dungeons DX [Nintendo Switch / Steam] Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Blending rogue-like mechanics with item crafting, Alchemic Dungeons DX is a game of endless variety. This deluxe version includes new characters, items and dungeons; the background music and visuals have also been enhanced!

Alchemic Dungeons DX launches globally on the Nintendo Switch eShop and Steam on 14th February!

Wishlist on Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1022610/Alchemic_Dungeons_DX/

Follow us on Twitter - https://twitter.com/FlyhighWorks_en
